    {
      "id": "engine-detail",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 795,
      "y": 755,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 220,
      "text": "Standard EngineRequest\n  (no catalog flag)\n\nStandard TF service flow:\n  1. shallow fetch @SHA\n  2. terraform init\n  3. terraform plan\n  4. terraform apply\n  5. extract outputs\n     (QSM_* outputs work)\n\ngRPC -> q-core:\n  sendTerraformResources\n  (output key/value pairs)\n\nNo engine changes needed\nfor catalog services",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
